cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.SE, cs.AI, cs.DB 

This paper is about semantics of logic programs, which is a core topic in programming languages and logic. Therefore, cs.PL (Programming Languages) and cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses program analysis and debugging, which are related to software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper mentions the use of fixpoint semantics, which is a technique used in databases (cs.DB).
